        "cel_dydaktyczny_eng": "Japanese language instruction from scratch. Students acquire Japanese proficiency enabling communication in most everyday situations and, to some extent, professional contexts, as well as expressing thoughts and opinions and understanding and producing short written texts and spoken statements on various topics. Students also learn about the culture, history, and everyday life of Japan and Japanese-speaking regions.",
